	(text "want hysteresis only as recovery for OTD\ndon't want load removal for UV ecovery (verify by simulating UV - how?)\nOCD1&2 delay good considering OCD2 = 26A\nload removal as a SCD may be needed for safety (this is perma set in the chip).\nwhat battery cell connector to use? screw terminal?\nPRES pin\nDouble check gnd pins placement"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
