	(text_box "Test Procedure:\n1. Simulate cells with 4 200R resistors\n2. Confirm shunts on J4 shorting pins 1 to 2 and 3 to 4\n3. Confirm shunts on J2 shorting pins 1 to 2\n4. Connect an 14.4V power supply across pin 1 and 5 on J1\n5. Enable power supply\n6. Check voltage on pack terminals is 15V (both FETs are on)\n7. Simulate load with a 5k 1/4W resistor\n8. Adjust supply to 17.5V to simulate overvoltage, check that pack voltage is approx. 600mV\n10. Adjust supply back to 15V to recover from overvoltage, check that pack voltage is the same as supply\n11. Remove shunt on pins 1-2 of J4 to simulate hot, check pack voltage is 0V and returns to normal when shunt re-installed\n12. Remove shunt on pins 3-4 of J4 to simulate cold, check pack voltage is 0V and returns to normal when shunt re-installed\n13. Adjust supply to 10V voltage to simulate undervoltage, check that pack voltage is 0V\n14. Adjust supply back to 15V to recover from undervoltage, observe pack voltage is the same as supply. If pack voltage is still 0V, load removal is needed to recover from undervoltage.\n    Remove load resistor and check that pack voltage is the same as supply"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at -107.315 207.645 0)
		(size 95.25 40.64)
		(margins 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525)
		(stroke
			(width 0)
			(type solid)
		)
		(fill
			(type none)
		)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left top)
		)
		(uuid "2ef2457d-72e3-4e9e-abdb-e5e0290d15d9")
	)
	(text_box "Notes:\n1. R_gs_chg = 3.3MΩ\n2. R_sense = 0.035V / 15A (OCD1) = 2.3mOhms \n3. OCDP resistor = 383k ±1% (180ms-90ms) (make swappable)\n4. CBI connected to VSS for self-balancing\n5. Leave CBO floating \n6. C_ini = 1uF\n7. R_vdd = 1kΩ\n8. C_vdd = 1uF\n9. R_ini = 100Ω for balancing current of 38mA\n10. PRES = high (to exit HIBERNATE) (could add a switch to enter HIBERBATE during transit)\n11. CCFG connected to AVDD for 4S\n12. Double check if D2 should be more than 16V, like 21V instead\n13. Extra care for for layout shunt res"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 0.635 216.535 0)
		(size 68.58 35.56)
		(margins 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525)
